    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors evaluated against MRL 5 requirements for Class III VAD device. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ initiated but input characterization incomplete. Overall credibility package does not meet requirements for absolute hemolysis prediction at MRL 5. Package submitted for regulatory review under the understanding that identified gaps must be resolved prior to final device submission.",
